{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/chips-membasmi-monster-di-google-play-indonesia-games-contest-2017/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"CHIPS Membasmi Monster di Google Play Indonesia Games Contest 2017","content":"<p>Meski belum lama dirilis, game CHIPS: Monster Tap berhasil terpilih menjadi salah satu dari 15 besar finalis <em>games</em> di Google Play Indonesia Games Contest lho! Mau tau keseruan apa aja saat tim CIAYO Games menempati salah satu booth di The Warehouse, Plaza Indonesia? Yuk disimak!</p>\n<p>Lokasi <em>booth</em> CHIPS: Monster Tap yang cukup strategis, membuat booth CHIPS selalu ramai. Apalagi warna kuningnya yang <em>eye catching </em>berhasil menjadi daya tarik tersendiri bagi pengunjung.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_2454\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2454\" data-attachment-id=\"2454\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/chips-membasmi-monster-di-google-play-indonesia-games-contest-2017/attachment/body6-10/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body6-9.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"body6\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body6-9-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body6-9.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-2454 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body6-9.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body6-9.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body6-9-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-2454\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Booth CHIPS: Monster Tap rame terus! (CIAYO Pictures)</p></div></p>\n<p>Pengunjung yang mendatangi booth CHIPS: Monster Tap akan langsung disambut oleh para developer. Ga cuma bisa main langsung dan dijelasin gamenya, tapi pengunjung boleh bertanya langsung mengenai <em>behind the scene</em> pembuatan game ini.</p>\n<p><div style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"2449\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/chips-membasmi-monster-di-google-play-indonesia-games-contest-2017/attachment/body1-11/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body1-10.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"body1\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body1-10-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body1-10.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-2449 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body1-10.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body1-10.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body1-10-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Bisa main langsung CHIPS Monster Tap di lokasi (CIAYO Pictures)</p></div></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_2455\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2455\" data-attachment-id=\"2455\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/chips-membasmi-monster-di-google-play-indonesia-games-contest-2017/attachment/body7-9/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body7-8.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"body7\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body7-8-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body7-8.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-2455 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body7-8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body7-8.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body7-8-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-2455\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Nata, salah satu member tim CIAYO Games saat berbincang dengan pengunjung. (CIAYO Pictures)</p></div></p>\n<p>Tak hanya <em>experience </em>yang didapatkan<em>, </em>pengunjung juga bisa membawa pulang berbagai macam <em>merchandise</em> berupa topi Chips, kipas, kaos dan beanie hat Crocket! (Wah oleh-olehnya banyak ya!)</p>\n<p>Acara puncak dari <em>event</em> ini adalah masing-masing developer game maju ke panggung untuk melakukan presentasi secara bergantian. Presentasi berisikan keunikan dari games, serta penjelasan mengapa finalis games pantas untuk menang. Presentasi CHIPS: Monster Tap diwakili oleh CTO CIAYO Games, Victorio Primadi. Beliau menjelaskan latar belakang dibuatnya <em>game</em> serta keunggulan game CHIPS: Monster Tap.</p>\n<p><span class=\"m_-3008492603474170130s1\">&#8220;Untuk gameplay, kami mengusung genre <em>idle clicker</em>, kami coba melakukan beberapa inovasi supaya gamenya terasa lebih variatif, salah satunya adalah menambahkan fase membangun robot sebelum memasuki fase pertarungan melawan monster-monster ganas nan imut!&#8221; begitu kata Victorio Primadi. </span><span class=\"m_-3008492603474170130s1\">&#8220;Harapan kami sebagai studio game adalah supaya game kami dapat dinikmati oleh gamer lokal dan mancanegara karena salah satu misi kami adalah membawa dan memperkenalkan konten-konten serta budaya Indonesia ke seluruh dunia.&#8221; tambahnya.</span></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_2452\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2452\" data-attachment-id=\"2452\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/chips-membasmi-monster-di-google-play-indonesia-games-contest-2017/attachment/body4-11/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body4-10.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"body4\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body4-10-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body4-10.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-2452 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body4-10.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body4-10.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body4-10-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-2452\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Victorio Primadi, CTO CIAYO Games sedang presentasi. (CIAYO Pictures)</p></div></p>\n<p>Sesi berikutnya merupakan sesi talkshow yang menghadirkan tiga panelist sekaligus yaitu, Muhammad Neil El Himam (BEKRAF) , Narenda Wicaksono (AGI) dan Andi Suryanto (Lyto). Mereka berbicara mengenai pentingnya event-event seperti ini untuk memicu semangat dan potensi developer dalam negeri agar semakin berkembang dan mampu bersaing dengan para developer global.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_2451\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2451\" data-attachment-id=\"2451\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/chips-membasmi-monster-di-google-play-indonesia-games-contest-2017/attachment/body3-9/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body3-8.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"body3\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body3-8-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body3-8.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-2451 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body3-8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body3-8.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body3-8-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-2451\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sesi talkshow sembari menunggu pengumuman pemenang (CIAYO Pictures)</p></div></p>\n<p>Saat pengumuman, CHIPS: Monster Tap belum beruntung untuk menempati posisi tiga besar. Namun dengan masuk ke dalam finalis 15 besar pun, merupakan prestasi yang sangat membanggakan bagi CIAYO Corp, mengingat game ini baru dirilis kurang lebih satu bulan. (Selamat para pemenang!)</p>\n<p>Kekalahan kali ini justru menjadi pemicu semangat tim CIAYO Games untuk terus berkarya! Buat <em>bro sis </em>yang penasaran dan belum nyobain keseruan CIAYO Games yuk cek keseruannya di <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/chammyland-diserang-monster-ayo-bantu-chips-crocket-dan-coco-dengan-main-chips-monster-tap/\">sini</a>. CHIPS: Monster Tap juga bisa di-<em>download</em> di <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ciayo.chipsmonstertap\">Android</a> dan <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/chips-monster-tap/id1199367972?mt=8\">iOS</a>!</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_2450\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2450\" data-attachment-id=\"2450\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/chips-membasmi-monster-di-google-play-indonesia-games-contest-2017/attachment/body2-10/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body2-9.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"body2\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body2-9-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body2-9.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-2450 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body2-9.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body2-9.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body2-9-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-2450\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Salam hangat dari tim CIAYO Games, terima kasih atas dukungannya. (CIAYO Pictures)</p></div></p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"49bb0358-b1cc-52ea-8caf-44764f65f0f0"}}}